<i>Gee, I'm glad I joined the Navy

102
00:07:16,778 --> 00:07:18,356
Two-sixteen.

103
00:07:18,530 --> 00:07:21,068
Halt. Good job.

104
00:07:21,241 --> 00:07:24,360
Ditch your helmets.
Get on your covers. Hurry up.

105
00:07:24,536 --> 00:07:27,702
Come on, move it.
Look sharp. Quickly.

106
00:07:27,872 --> 00:07:30,244
Class, left face.

107
00:07:31,584 --> 00:07:33,493
Log bridges. Let's go, let's go.

108
00:07:33,670 --> 00:07:35,247
Go, go, go.

109
00:07:35,421 --> 00:07:37,710
Get them up, ladies.
Get them up, get them up.

110
00:07:37,882 --> 00:07:39,756
Hurry up. Ready.

111
00:07:39,926 --> 00:07:41,586
Begin.

112
00:07:41,761 --> 00:07:43,504
Any of you little kittens wanna quit?

113
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,759
No, sir.

114
00:07:44,931 --> 00:07:46,555
I've got cocoa and cookies

115
00:07:46,724 --> 00:07:49,180
for anybody who wants to cash in
their chips and ring the bell.

116
00:07:49,352 --> 00:07:50,597
I've got cake for the officers.

117
00:07:50,770 --> 00:07:52,893
- Anybody?
- No, sir.

118
00:07:53,064 --> 00:07:54,772
What do you think this is? <i>GI Jane?

119
00:07:55,233 --> 00:07:56,312
No, sir.

120
00:07:56,484 --> 00:07:57,682
Do you wanna stay and fight?

121
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,023
Hoorah, sir.

122
00:07:59,195 --> 00:08:01,401
- Let me hear you.
- Hoorah, sir.

123
00:08:01,572 --> 00:08:03,648
A SEAL must focus on a mission,

124
00:08:03,825 --> 00:08:07,240
must accomplish his goals
regardless of his injuries.

125
00:08:07,411 --> 00:08:09,949
The pain, the heat, the cold.

126
00:08:10,122 --> 00:08:12,578
We're here to train your minds
as well as your bodies.

127
00:08:12,792 --> 00:08:15,034
Your mind can teach your body
how to function.

128
00:08:15,211 --> 00:08:19,422
Your strength is not in your muscles,
it's in your brains.

129
00:08:19,590 --> 00:08:21,666
In your brains.

130
00:08:21,842 --> 00:08:25,923
Why don't you get your brains to get
your legs to do another five laps?

131
00:08:26,097 --> 00:08:27,639
Let's go.

132
00:08:29,225 --> 00:08:31,264
- Move it. Let's go.
- Move it. Move it.

133
00:08:31,435 --> 00:08:33,891
- Hurry up. Let's go. Hurry up.
- Move it. Move it.

134
00:08:34,063 --> 00:08:35,225
Hurry up, ladies.

135
00:08:35,398 --> 00:08:38,185
Left face.

136
00:08:38,359 --> 00:08:40,268
About time.

137
00:08:40,444 --> 00:08:43,398
- <i>GI grits and GI gravy</i>
- Lt. Rivers.

138
00:08:43,572 --> 00:08:46,407
